{"tid":2113854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳玉娥再戰新東！","createTime":"2020-07-18T11:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T00:07:46.000Z","uid":84308,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"2d683115eeb6a92a0d7c1561c8156be41994ab2d","tid":2113854,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"立法會換屆選舉今日起接受報名，除主流政治人物外，亦可見一些熟悉的臉孔。<br />\n<br />\n選管會公佈的資料顯示，激進親中派陳玉娥再戰新界東。她曾稱讚前特首梁振英太完美，但最受關注的實是四年前選舉與公民黨楊岳橋譜起的「娥頸橋之戀」。<br />\n<br />\n知名網絡人物「龍心」亦已報名參選新界東，相信兩人會為選舉論壇和其他活動增添不少樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n另外值得留意人稱「夏蕙姨」的黃夏蕙有意出選香港島，現於社交網站公開收集提名，不難想像她會與熱血公民派出的「法子」莊芷茵上演一場激烈的選美戰。<br />\n<br />\n圖一來源：香港01<br />\n<br />\n#香港政治 #立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1017435307/437280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1017435307%2F437280&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=fac7f535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1017435307/437280</a>"},{"pid":"b3f4cda9c5dad3280b7ac150e700d993ee39eb13","tid":2113854,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠提名先"},{"pid":"23b95c2ba3a32b117043786b627b068d71c43d81","tid":2113854,"uid":39492,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"新東成撚日咁多騎呢怪出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67546e98e1483ed3e3d31461f3d99ccb21539d06","tid":2113854,"uid":66331,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"無參加初選唔投<br />\nJ左佢幾年都係咁話"},{"pid":"20d952b8d267a1cd03cc7cf06a67a4b7f612f357","tid":2113854,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67546e98e1483ed3e3d31461f3d99ccb21539d06","tid":2113854,"uid":66331,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"無參加初選唔投<br />\nJ左佢幾年都係咁話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:40:50.000Z","ms